snippet.title: Amber Heard Interview -- The Rum Diary | Empire Magazine
snippet.description:
Subscribe to our channel: http://bit.ly/EmpireSub
Amber Heard stars in The Rum Diary alongside Johnny Depp in Bruce Robinson's adaptation of Hunter S. Thompson's novel. But the question is: what's scarier, working with Depp or an interview with Empire?
